+## Anthropic Claude built-ins (zero config)
+
+After `grok anthropic login`, Grok automatically adds the built-in
+`anthropic/*` catalog (the adaptive-thinking Claude generation: Opus 4.6–4.8,
+Sonnet 4.6/5, Fable 5). No `[model.*]` configuration is needed:
+
+```
+/model anthropic/claude-opus-4-8:high
+/model anthropic/claude-sonnet-5:max
+```
+
+The provider prefix chooses the Anthropic OAuth credential and Messages
+backend; the optional `:effort` suffix chooses the adaptive thinking effort
+(`low` through `max`; native `xhigh` on Opus 4.7/4.8, Sonnet 5, and Fable 5,
+elsewhere `xhigh` resolves to `max`). See
+[Authentication](02-authentication.md#anthropic-claude-with-a-promax-plan).
+
